A node in ruby

Fully working ruby node for blusteromatic.

Init script:
	# cp init_script /etc/init.d/blusteromatic_node
	# chmod +x !$

Redhat:		chkconfig --level 345 blusteromatic_node on
Debian/ubuntu:	update-rc.d -f blusteromatic_node defaults
Gentoo:		rc-update add blusteromatic_node default

